is.ru.honn.rutube.service

Class UserServiceStub

  • java.lang.Object
    • is.ru.honn.rutube.service.UserServiceStub
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UserService

    public class UserServiceStub
extends java.lang.Object
implements UserService
    Version:
    1.0, 28/09/16. This class contains a setter function for the user list as well as getter functions where you can either get the whole list of users or a single user with a specific id. The class also contains the addUser function which adds a user to the user list and returns the size of the list.
    Author:
    Steinar Marinó Hilmarsson and Egill Gautur Steingrímsson.

        public int addUser(User user)
            throws ServiceException
        This function adds a user to the user list and returns the size of the list or throws an exception. Exception is thrown if some of the attributes are in use. Those include the id, name, email or display name.
        Specified by:
        addUser in interface UserService
        Parameters:
        user - The user.
        Returns:
        The size of the user list.
        Throws:
